Our Story

Established in 1985, DMC World is the world’s longest-running and most prestigious DJ competition on the planet. Period.  Since its launch, the Championships have created such turntable superstars as A-Trak, Cash Money, Craze, DJ Fly, DJ Kentaro, Mix Master Mike, Netik and Roc Raida with entrants arriving from over 75 countries.Winning the DMC World Title is the biggest accolade for any Turntablist, putting on the famous DMC World Champion Jacket is the biggest prize in DJing.
